name: collection.js-a-Javascript-alternative-of-Java-collection-framework
description: As JavaScript is growing in the server side domain quite faster, to store access and manipulate data we feel the need of a strong framework in JavaScript like Collection in Java. Providing all sort of data structures, utility classes, various sorting & searching functions under a single shed will help users to develop product faster and easier.
author: Dip Bhattacharjee
